{"tid":1882331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"短時間反cup youtube戰線方法：區議員","createTime":"2020-02-16T07:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T17:11:22.000Z","uid":28718,"like":99,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"8c12efe8a3a5140d051b7a987e2024368fe44650","tid":1882331,"uid":28718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"1. k100成班人有中共backup，統籌度橋剪片全部同一班人，靠素人同佢抗衡係好難，時間金錢都唔夠對手多<br />\n<br />\n2. 有人話係吸後生觀眾，呢點我唔同意，後生9成黃，佢要吸嘅係中立同淺藍，令佢地更藍，用youtube打我地嘅連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n3. 區議員做，已有知名度，有政黨backup，可以做到同對家同樣效果<br />\n<br />\n4. 連登仔覺得對家啲片咁都幾十萬views，咁係咪應該諗如果係仇栩欣、梁凱晴之類係可以輕鬆過百萬？<br />\n<br />\n5. 非常重要，對家一定會賣廣告推藍色經濟圈，所以呢樣野區議員都一定要做<br />\n<br />\n6. 區議員肯做，youtube戰線就有得贏，你就變黃絲kol，就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"340b01d6ad2e3929d081c6b26c76d59cc9dd5d7a","tid":1882331,"uid":28718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:30:39.000Z","msg":"推到所有區議員睇到"},{"pid":"37aff9911a999a3b6830e2dc62928a2afb8752ec","tid":1882331,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"鄺仔做緊，支持左未？<br />\n<br />\n鄺仔出咗新片，你地like咗未？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1882254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1882254</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6daa6023714b25416b2bab84e78a1b8233b7cb67","tid":1882331,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e1c55607d047f652795962a8ed194720f31aa0","tid":1882331,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ddbde99aa2d350567facf35c0ed024096c2193","tid":1882331,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T07:33:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人推俾區議員"},{